I have been to this Domino's (in Lakeview) because it is close to my house several times in the past two weeks.  I never knew what a little gem this place was and so affordable! Tonight I placed an order online, as opposed to going there and picking it up myself, and there was a little snafu with the delivery driver.  When I called to complain, the manager remained courteous and gracious and even gave me a large discount for "my troubles".  I called her back and apologized for being such a ginormous beatch!  I should have been more understanding.  This place is packed with orders all the time and there is bound to be mistakes.  Nevertheless, she was gracious and very generous with her discount.  The food was delicious (as usual) and again, you cannot beat the prices and they really do have your food ready in less than 30 minutes!  Amazing service, food and price!  Domino's has won my heart over other more expensive eateries!
